{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "dialogueType": "companion",
  "_comment": "Plan 2 T13 — Field Medic archetype dialog. Three archetypes: compassionate, pragmatic, pious. Loaded by CompanionDialogueCatalog. Mirrors companion_sergeant.json node-id structure. Token usage: {PLAYER_NAME} for warmth/care; {PLAYER_RANK} sparingly where station genuinely fits (medic less rank-fixated than sergeant); {LORD_NAME} when referring to the enlisted commander; {COMPANION_FIRST_NAME} for compassionate/pragmatic player options, {COMPANION_NAME} for pious (honorifics like 'Brother'/'Sister').",
  "nodes": [

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_intro_greeting",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_greeting_compassionate",
      "text": "Another new face. I hope I won't see too much of you on my table, {PLAYER_NAME}.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "compassionate", "is_introduced": false },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_warm",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_opt_warm",
          "text": "I'll try to keep clear of it, {COMPANION_FIRST_NAME}.",
          "tooltip": "Greet warmly (+2 relationship)",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": 2 }
        },
        {
          "id": "intro_brave",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_opt_brave",
          "text": "I'll try not to bleed on your floor.",
          "tooltip": "Bluff (no change)",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": 0 }
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_intro_greeting",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_greeting_pragmatic",
      "text": "Name and weight, {PLAYER_RANK}. If you bleed badly I want to know how much wine and bandage you'll cost me.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pragmatic", "is_introduced": false },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_direct",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_opt_direct",
          "text": "{PLAYER_NAME}. I'll come back when I have something useful for you.",
          "tooltip": "Match the bluntness (+2 relationship)",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": 2 }
        },
        {
          "id": "intro_offended",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_opt_offended",
          "text": "Charming bedside manner, {COMPANION_FIRST_NAME}.",
          "tooltip": "Push back (-1 relationship)",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": -1 }
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_intro_greeting",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_greeting_pious",
      "text": "The gods sent you here, {PLAYER_NAME}. Whether to live or to die is theirs to decide. Mine is only to clean the wounds.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pious", "is_introduced": false },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_reverent",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_opt_reverent",
          "text": "Then I'll thank them for the careful hands, {COMPANION_NAME}.",
          "tooltip": "Match the reverence (+2 relationship)",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": 2 }
        },
        {
          "id": "intro_secular",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_opt_secular",
          "text": "I'd rather rely on your hands than on theirs.",
          "tooltip": "Brush off the piety (-1 relationship)",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": -1 }
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack_compassionate",
      "text": "Mind your footing in the line, {PLAYER_NAME}. A turned ankle takes longer to heal than most boys believe.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "compassionate" },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_ack_close",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack_opt_close",
          "text": "{COMPANION_FIRST_NAME}.",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack_pragmatic",
      "text": "Good. Boil your water before you drink it, {PLAYER_NAME}. That alone keeps half my patients off the table.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pragmatic" },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_ack_close",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack_opt_close",
          "text": "Noted.",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack_pious",
      "text": "Walk with the rites, {PLAYER_NAME}. The body endures longer when the spirit is settled.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pious" },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_ack_close",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_intro_ack_opt_close",
          "text": "I'll try.",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_root",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_root_default",
      "text": "Are you hurt, {PLAYER_NAME}, or is this a social visit?",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic" },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "root_healing",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_root_opt_healing",
          "text": "How do you keep men on their feet out here?",
          "tooltip": "Ask about field medicine",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_topic_healing"
        },
        {
          "id": "root_horror",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_root_opt_horror",
          "text": "How do you bear all of it?",
          "tooltip": "Ask about the cost of war",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_topic_horror"
        },
        {
          "id": "root_wounded",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_root_opt_wounded",
          "text": "How are the wounded from the last fight?",
          "tooltip": "Ask after recent casualties",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_topic_wounded",
          "requirements": { "has_recent_battle": true }
        },
        {
          "id": "root_advice",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_root_opt_advice",
          "text": "Any advice for someone in the line?",
          "tooltip": "Ask for mentorship",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_topic_advice"
        },
        {
          "id": "root_leave",
          "textId": "companion_field_medic_root_opt_leave",
          "text": "Carry on, healer.",
          "next_node": "companion_field_medic_goodbye"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_healing",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_healing_compassionate",
      "text": "Warm broth, dry blankets, and a hand on the shoulder. Half of healing is letting them know someone is still there, {PLAYER_NAME}.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "compassionate" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "healing_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_healing_opt_close", "text": "I'll remember that.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_healing",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_healing_pragmatic",
      "text": "Triage by minutes, not by sympathy. Fast bleeders first, broken bones last, the dying set aside. Wine cleans wounds; prayer does not.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pragmatic" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "healing_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_healing_opt_close", "text": "Understood.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_healing",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_healing_pious",
      "text": "I clean the wound and speak the rites. The gods take or leave each soul as they will. The hands and the words are mine to give.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pious" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "healing_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_healing_opt_close", "text": "Thank you, {COMPANION_NAME}.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_horror",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_horror_compassionate",
      "text": "Some nights I don't, {PLAYER_NAME}. I sit with a cup of wine and let the names come back. Then I go again in the morning, because someone has to.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "compassionate" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "horror_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_horror_opt_close", "text": "I'm sorry.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_horror",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_horror_pragmatic",
      "text": "It's wounds and ratios. A man with a deep belly cut at sundown won't see morning. I save the ones I can save and stop counting the rest.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pragmatic" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "horror_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_horror_opt_close", "text": "Plain enough.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_horror",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_horror_pious",
      "text": "Each death is owed somewhere — to the gods, to the soil, to {LORD_NAME} who called us out. I tend what I can and leave the ledger to those above.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pious" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "horror_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_horror_opt_close", "text": "A heavy ledger.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_wounded",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_wounded_compassionate",
      "text": "Two will walk again by week's end, {PLAYER_NAME}. The young one with the leg wound is asking for his mother. I sat with him an hour.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "compassionate", "has_recent_battle": true },
      "options": [
        { "id": "wounded_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_wounded_opt_close", "text": "I'll look in on him.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_wounded",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_wounded_pragmatic",
      "text": "Five stable, two questionable, one gone before the bandages were out. Stitch counts within expectations for an engagement of {LORD_NAME}'s size.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pragmatic", "has_recent_battle": true },
      "options": [
        { "id": "wounded_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_wounded_opt_close", "text": "Thank you.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_wounded",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_wounded_pious",
      "text": "Three will live. One is past the rites. I lit a candle for him and washed the others' hands. The gods know their names now, {PLAYER_NAME}.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pious", "has_recent_battle": true },
      "options": [
        { "id": "wounded_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_wounded_opt_close", "text": "May he rest.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_advice",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_advice_compassionate",
      "text": "Drink water, sleep when you can, and don't hide a fever from me, {PLAYER_NAME}. A small thing left alone becomes a grave.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "compassionate" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "advice_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_advice_opt_close", "text": "I'll remember.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_advice",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_advice_pragmatic",
      "text": "Boil your water. Burn your bandages. If a wound smells sweet, it's already won. The rest is luck, {PLAYER_RANK}.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pragmatic" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "advice_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_advice_opt_close", "text": "Useful.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_topic_advice",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_advice_pious",
      "text": "Walk with what's owed and what's given, {PLAYER_NAME}. Speak the rites at sunset. The body holds longer when the soul knows it isn't alone.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic", "archetype": "pious" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "advice_close", "textId": "companion_field_medic_advice_opt_close", "text": "Thank you, {COMPANION_NAME}.", "next_node": "companion_field_medic_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_field_medic_goodbye",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_field_medic_goodbye_default",
      "text": "Stay clear of my table, {PLAYER_NAME}.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "field_medic" },
      "options": []
    }
  ]
}
